Funke Akindele and JJC Skillz | Pulse Due to the breakout of the virus, the federal government banned the gathering of more than 20 people in the same space and also restricted movement in some parts of the country. However, yesterday, Funke Akindele and husband, JJC Skillz, threw a birthday party with lots of people in attendance. She later made a video to apologise, this was before the Police Force arrested her for violating rules that were in place. Below are some reactions to this news:          